      • test_addTermsFiltersAlreadyAssigned

        public void test_addTermsFiltersAlreadyAssigned()
        Unit test verifies that BigdataValues whose term identifiers have already been assigned are unchanged by LexiconRelation.addTerms(BigdataValue[], int, boolean).

        Note: BNodes are not tested for this property since they will be assigned a new term identifier each time. Blank nodes are ONLY made self-consistent within a canonicalizing mapping imposed for some blank node context, e.g., a source document that is being parsed.
